                <h1>Change PowerPoint Background Color: Easy Steps</h1>
                <p>To change the background color on PowerPoint, go to the slide you want to modify. Click on the "Design" tab and select "Format Background." Choose "Solid Fill" and pick your desired color. This change can apply to the current slide or all slides by clicking "Apply to All." Save your presentation for the updates to take effect.</p>
